title: Tourists may want to leave: Category 5 hurricane approaching !
text:
Click here for information and nomination Tourists may want to leave: Category 5 hurricane approaching ! 
Visitors may want to consider leaving at this time. Difficult to overstate how horrific Hurricane Hurricane Patricia looks from satellite right now. The category 5 Hurricane is scheduled to make landfall in Mexico on Friday. 
Experts say it's a "potentially catastrophic hurricane." It is expected to weaken by Friday, and should make landfall on the Pacific coast near Punta San Telmo late in the day still as an extremely dangerous storm. Oct 23, 2015
